snippet.title: SNES Longplay [442] Ashita no Joe
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: SCHLAUCHI

Anime based boxing game - not too bad!
In order to get the best ending, you have to survive the last fight without knocking out the other boxer! -
